2025-08-08 23:16:45\"},{\"content\":\"You can use JavaScript in mobile and desktop applications.\",\"translation\":\"Puede usar JavaScript en aplicaciones m\\u00f3viles y de escritorio.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:16:52\"},{\"content\":\"It is not just for websites, but for many platforms.\",\"translation\":\"No es solo para sitios web, sino para muchas plataformas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:16:57\"},{\"content\":\"That makes it a great skill to learn today.\",\"translation\":\"Eso hace que sea una gran habilidad para aprender hoy.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:02\"},{\"content\":\"JavaScript also includes many built-in objects and functions.\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript tambi\\u00e9n incluye muchos objetos y funciones incorporados.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:07\"},{\"content\":\"You can work with text, numbers, and even dates easily.\",\"translation\":\"Puede trabajar con texto, n\\u00fameros e incluso fechas f\\u00e1cilmente.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:13\"},{\"content\":\"One of its strengths is working with the DOM.\",\"translation\":\"Una de sus fortalezas es trabajar con el DOM.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:19\"},{\"content\":\"The DOM is the structure of a webpage in the browser.\",\"translation\":\"El DOM es la estructura de una p\\u00e1gina web en el navegador.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:23\"},{\"content\":\"With JavaScript, you can change a webpage in real time.\",\"translation\":\"Con JavaScript, puede cambiar una p\\u00e1gina web en tiempo real.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:27\"},{\"content\":\"You can add text, remove images, or update styles instantly.\",\"translation\":\"Puede agregar texto, eliminar im\\u00e1genes o actualizar estilos al instante.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:33\"},{\"content\":\"You can add text, remove images, or update styles instantly.\",\"translation\":\"Puede agregar texto, eliminar im\\u00e1genes o actualizar estilos al instante.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:17:35\"