(169, 22, 'The old town was full', 'El casco antiguo estaba lleno', 'The old town was full\r\nThe old town was full of narrow streets, tall buildings, and small hidden gardens. My friend invited me to visit her apartment, and she told me that I would love it. When I finally reached the place, I saw her smiling face waiting for me. She gave me a warm hug, and I felt truly happy to see her again. Her home was not very large, but it was bright, clean, and beautifully decorated. She had painted the walls in soft blue, and her books were arranged neatly on the wide wooden shelves.\r\n\r\nShe showed me her favorite room, which was her study. It had a comfortable chair, a shiny desk, and a tall window with a lovely view of the quiet street below. She asked me to sit down and relax, and I accepted. She made us some hot tea and brought delicious homemade cookies. While I was drinking, she told me stories about her childhood, her family, and her travels. Listening to her made me feel calm, curious, and inspired.\r\n\r\nLater, we walked together through the lively market near her home. The air was filled with the smell of fresh bread, sweet fruits, and spicy herbs. We passed by friendly vendors who offered us samples of their products. One man gave her a ripe apple and asked her to taste it. Another woman smiled at me and offered me some fresh cheese. We thanked them, and we bought a small basket of colorful fruits to share later.\r\n\r\nOn the way back, we met her neighbor. He was an old but strong man with kind eyes. He greeted us warmly and asked us if we needed any help carrying the basket. We told him that we could manage it, but we appreciated his kindness. I could see how much she respected him, and he clearly admired her as well. Their relationship seemed natural, simple, and honest.\r\n\r\nWhen we returned to her apartment, we prepared a light dinner together. She cooked rice and vegetables while I cut the bread and set the table. We laughed about silly things and remembered old times. It was a peaceful evening, and it reminded me how important it is to spend time with people we care about. Her friendship felt like a precious gift, and I promised myself to visit her again soon.', '[{\"content\":\"The old town was full of narrow streets, tall buildings, and small hidden gardens.\",\"translation\":\"El casco antiguo estaba lleno de calles estrechas, edificios altos y peque\\u00f1os jardines escondidos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:39:10\"},{\"content\":\"My friend invited me to visit her apartment, and she told me that I would love it.\",\"translation\":\"Mi amiga me invit\\u00f3 a visitar su apartamento y me dijo que me encantar\\u00eda.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:39:29\"},{\"content\":\"When I finally reached the place, I saw her smiling face waiting for me.\",\"translation\":\"Cuando por fin llegu\\u00e9 al lugar, vi su cara sonriente esper\\u00e1ndome.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:40:05\"},{\"content\":\"Ten\\u00eda  una silla c\\u00f3moda , un escritorio brillante y una ventana alta con una hermosa vista de la tranquila calle de  abajo.\",\"translation\":\"It had a comfortable chair, a bright desk and a tall window with a beautiful view of the quiet street below.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:40:33\"},{\"content\":\"Ella me mostr\\u00f3 su habitaci\\u00f3n favorita , que era su estudio.\",\"translation\":\"She showed me her favorite room, which was her study.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:40:48\"},{\"content\":\"Ella  me pidi\\u00f3  que me sentara y me relajara, y acept\\u00e9 .\",\"translation\":\"She asked me to sit down and relax, and I agreed.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:40:49\"},{\"content\":\"Ten\\u00eda una silla c\\u00f3moda , un escritorio brillante y una ventana alta con una hermosa vista de la tranquila calle de abajo.\",\"translation\":\"It had a comfortable chair, a bright desk and a tall window with a beautiful view of the quiet street below.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-26 03:40:51\"},{\"conten